title: 13 min Breathwork & Meditation Practice | Pranayama Techniques | Stress & Anxiety Relief
description:
Use this breath practice for a clear, calm, and energized mind. This is for those who feel ungrounded, overworked, or mentally overstimulated. Feel free to do this session seated on a block or pillow or lying down. Would love to know how you felt 🤍
